The paper discusses the use of Artificial Neural Networks (ANN) to predict the abrasion resistance of solution polymerized styrene-butadiene rubber (SSBR) based composites. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.NE, cs.LG, and cs.AI. The paper also involves statistical analysis and modeling, which could be categorized under cs.MS. Additionally, the paper discusses the practical applications of the SSBR-based composites, which could fall under cs.SE.
